    "id": "converse-api",
    "subject": "Add /api/converse endpoint for multi-turn AI tutoring conversation about today's cards",
    "status": "pending",
    "description": "POST /api/converse/start: initializes a conversation session about today's due cards using SRSProtocol. The system prompt instructs the AI to act as a tutor discussing the material, not just Q&A. POST /api/converse/turn: sends a user message, appends to history, returns AI response. Conversation stored in data/conversation.json per-date. GET /api/converse: returns current conversation state. The conversation starter prompt summarizes today's due topics and invites discussion. Conversation history is included in each turn so the AI has full context.",
